3. Portrait and Horizontal mode
    https://api.flutter.dev/flutter/widgets/MediaQuery-class.html
    A. Use MediaQuery:
        MediaQuery.of(context).size; //screen size,
        MediaQuery.of(context).orientation;  //orientation,
        MediaQuery.of(context).textScaleFactor //Font size
        etc.
